data.name: SqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT nID, nJobID, dCreateRecord, nVendorID, sPONum, sShipTo1, sShipTo2, sShipto3, sShipToCity, sShipToState, sShipToZip, sShiptoCounty, nBoxes, dPODate, sTerms, dRequired, sEnteredBy, nTotal, sVia, sFOB, nRetailSale, nSaleAccount, nRetailFreight, sConf, nAdd, DREC, DDEL, SRECNOTES, SDELNOTES, DFAXED, nAccount, nInvNo, nCheckNo, dSimply, bSimply, nTruck, sFilter, sBackOrder, sItems, sItemDesc, sPOType, nsalesadjust, sAdjustReason, sCurActNote, nPOSort FROM tPOHeader

data.name: SqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO tPOHeader(nJobID, dCreateRecord, nVendorID, sPONum, sShipTo1, sShipTo2, sShipto3, sShipToCity, sShipToState, sShipToZip, sShiptoCounty, nBoxes, dPODate, sTerms, dRequired, sEnteredBy, nTotal, sVia, sFOB, nRetailSale, nSaleAccount, nRetailFreight, sConf, nAdd, DREC, DDEL, SRECNOTES, SDELNOTES, DFAXED, nAccount, nInvNo, nCheckNo, dSimply, bSimply, nTruck, sFilter, sBackOrder, sItems, sItemDesc, sPOType, nsalesadjust, sAdjustReason, sCurActNote, nPOSort) VALUES (@nJobID, @dCreateRecord, @nVendorID, @sPONum, @sShipTo1, @sShipTo2, @sShipto3, @sShipToCity, @sShipToState, @sShipToZip, @sShiptoCounty, @nBoxes, @dPODate, @sTerms, @dRequired, @sEnteredBy, @nTotal, @sVia, @sFOB, @nRetailSale, @nSaleAccount, @nRetailFreight, @sConf, @nAdd, @DREC, @DDEL, @SRECNOTES, @SDELNOTES, @DFAXED, @nAccount, @nInvNo, @nCheckNo, @dSimply, @bSimply, @nTruck, @sFilter, @sBackOrder, @sItems, @sItemDesc, @sPOType, @nsalesadjust, @sAdjustReason, @sCurActNote, @nPOSort); SELECT nID, nJobID, dCreateRecord, nVendorID, sPONum, sShipTo1, sShipTo2, sShipto3, sShipToCity, sShipToState, sShipToZip, sShiptoCounty, nBoxes, dPODate, sTerms, dRequired, sEnteredBy, nTotal, sVia, sFOB, nRetailSale, nSaleAccount, nRetailFreight, sConf, nAdd, DREC, DDEL, SRECNOTES, SDELNOTES, DFAXED, nAccount, nInvNo, nCheckNo, dSimply, bSimply, nTruck, sFilter, sBackOrder, sItems, sItemDesc, sPOType, nsalesadjust, sAdjustReason, sCurActNote, nPOSort FROM tPOHeader WHERE (nID = @@IDENTITY)

data.name: SqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE tPOHeader SET DREC = @DREC, SRECNOTES = @SRECNOTES, DFAXED = @DFAXED, nTruck = @nTruck, sBackOrder = @sBackOrder WHERE (nID = @Original_nID) AND (DFAXED = @Original_DFAXED OR @Original_DFAXED IS NULL AND DFAXED IS NULL) AND (DREC = @Original_DREC OR @Original_DREC IS NULL AND DREC IS NULL) AND (SRECNOTES = @Original_SRECNOTES) AND (nTruck = @Original_nTruck) AND (sBackOrder = @Original_sBackOrder); SELECT nID, nJobID, dCreateRecord, nVendorID, sPONum, sShipTo1, sShipTo2, sShipto3, sShipToCity, sShipToState, sShipToZip, sShiptoCounty, nBoxes, dPODate, sTerms, dRequired, sEnteredBy, nTotal, sVia, sFOB, nRetailSale, nSaleAccount, nRetailFreight, sConf, nAdd, DREC, DDEL, SRECNOTES, SDELNOTES, DFAXED, nAccount, nInvNo, nCheckNo, dSimply, bSimply, nTruck, sFilter, sBackOrder, sItems, sItemDesc, sPOType, nsalesadjust, sAdjustReason, sCurActNote, nPOSort FROM tPOHeader WHERE (nID = @nID)

data.name: SqlCommand5.CommandText
data.value: SELECT nID, nJobID, dCreateRecord, nVendorID, sPONum, sShipTo1, sShipTo2, sShipto3, sShipToCity, sShipToState, sShipToZip, sShiptoCounty, nBoxes, dPODate, sTerms, dRequired, sEnteredBy, nTotal, sVia, sFOB, nRetailSale, nSaleAccount, nRetailFreight, sConf, nAdd, DREC, DDEL, SRECNOTES, SDELNOTES, DFAXED, nAccount, nInvNo, nCheckNo, dSimply, bSimply, nTruck, sFilter, sBackOrder, sItems, sItemDesc, sPOType, nsalesadjust, sAdjustReason, sCurActNote, nPOSort FROM tPOHeader WHERE (dRequired >= @STARTDATE) AND (dRequired <= @ENDDATE) ORDER BY nVendorID, nTruck, CASE WHEN ISNUMERIC(SUBSTRING(sPONum, 1, 5)) = 1 THEN substring(sPONum, 1, 5) ELSE '0' + substring(sPONum, 1, 4) END, nPOSort

data.name: SqlCommand6.CommandText
data.value: SELECT dbo.tPOLine.* FROM dbo.tPOLine INNER JOIN dbo.tPOHeader ON dbo.tPOLine.nPOID = dbo.tPOHeader.nID WHERE (dbo.tPOHeader.dRequired >= @STARTDATE) AND (dbo.tPOHeader.dRequired <= @ENDDATE) ORDER BY dbo.tPOHeader.nVendorID, dbo.tPOLine.nPOID, dbo.tPOLine.nLineNumber

data.name: SqlCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT nID, nJobID, dCreateRecord, nVendorID, sPONum, sShipTo1, sShipTo2, sShipto3, sShipToCity, sShipToState, sShipToZip, sShiptoCounty, nBoxes, dPODate, sTerms, dRequired, sEnteredBy, nTotal, sVia, sFOB, nRetailSale, nSaleAccount, nRetailFreight, sConf, nAdd, DREC, DDEL, SRECNOTES, SDELNOTES, DFAXED, nAccount, nInvNo, nCheckNo, dSimply, bSimply, nTruck, sFilter, sBackOrder, sItems, sItemDesc, sPOType, nsalesadjust, sAdjustReason, sCurActNote, nPOSort FROM tPOHeader WHERE (dRequired >= @STARTDATE) AND (dRequired <= @ENDDATE) AND (nVendorID = @nVendorID) ORDER BY nVendorID, nTruck, CASE WHEN ISNUMERIC(SUBSTRING(sPONum, 1, 5)) = 1 THEN substring(sPONum, 1, 5) ELSE '0' + substring(sPONum, 1, 4) END, nPOSort

data.name: SqlCommand2.CommandText
data.value: SELECT tPOLine.nPOID, tPOLine.nLineNumber, tPOLine.sType, tPOLine.sDesc, tPOLine.nCost, tPOLine.nAccountID, tPOLine.sReceived FROM tPOLine INNER JOIN tPOHeader ON tPOLine.nPOID = tPOHeader.nID WHERE (tPOHeader.dRequired >= @STARTDATE) AND (tPOHeader.dRequired <= @ENDDATE) AND (tPOHeader.nVendorID = @nvendorid) ORDER BY tPOHeader.nVendorID, tPOLine.nPOID, tPOLine.nLineNumber

data.name: SqlCommand3.CommandText
data.value: SELECT nID, nJobID, dCreateRecord, nVendorID, sPONum, sShipTo1, sShipTo2, sShipto3, sShipToCity, sShipToState, sShipToZip, sShiptoCounty, nBoxes, dPODate, sTerms, dRequired, sEnteredBy, nTotal, sVia, sFOB, nRetailSale, nSaleAccount, nRetailFreight, sConf, nAdd, DREC, DDEL, SRECNOTES, SDELNOTES, DFAXED, nAccount, nInvNo, nCheckNo, dSimply, bSimply, nTruck, sFilter, sBackOrder, sItems, sItemDesc, sPOType, nsalesadjust, sAdjustReason, sCurActNote, nPOSort FROM tPOHeader WHERE (sConf = '') ORDER BY nVendorID, nTruck, CASE WHEN ISNUMERIC(SUBSTRING(sPONum, 1, 5)) = 1 THEN substring(sPONum, 1, 5) ELSE '0' + substring(sPONum, 1, 4) END, nPOSort

data.name: SqlCommand4.CommandText
data.value: SELECT tPOLine.nPOID, tPOLine.nLineNumber, tPOLine.sType, tPOLine.sDesc, tPOLine.nCost, tPOLine.nAccountID, tPOLine.sReceived FROM tPOLine INNER JOIN tPOHeader ON tPOLine.nPOID = tPOHeader.nID WHERE (tPOHeader.sConf = '') ORDER BY tPOHeader.nVendorID, tPOLine.nPOID, tPOLine.nLineNumber
